    "description": "Chugokukogyo Co.,Ltd. manufactures and sells high voltage, steel structure, and facility equipment in Japan. The company offers LP gas containers, LP gas storage tanks, cylinders, and bulk storage tanks, and composite containers; steel, aluminum alloy, fluorocarbon, and other containers; and corrosive, toxic, and other special gas cylinders, as well as designs, constructs, and inspects LP gas filling plants. It also provides inner cover for annealing furnace; can manufacturing equipment, including data recorder enclosure and pressure transformer vessel; and other steel structural products. In addition, the company offers feed distribution products, such as FRP feed tanks, feed containers, feed transfer stations, and silage silos; livestock equipment and products comprising wet feeders and pipe barns; BM method and fine mist deodorizing devices; environmental conservation facility equipment; fisheries equipment and materials, which include aquaculture, breeding, and experimental tanks; and FRP pharmaceutical tanks, covers, automotive parts, vehicle wash basin units, and other FRP products for plants. Further, it provides plastic containers. The company was incorporated in 1950 and is headquartered in Kure, Japan."
